title: Francis Ellis: Harvard Man
description:
Kippy and Foley are back with a hot one featuring Francis Ellis. Francis talks going to Harvard, having a little bit of cash, and skiing. You know Francis Ellis from Barstool Sports, Brobile, and ad host of Oops Podcast! 




Originally Aired on www.GasdigitalNetwork.com on October 20th, 2020




Follow Kevin: https://www.instagram.com/kevinryancomedy/

Follow Foley: https://www.instagram.com/foleygrams/




Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the test.




Steal shampoo from hotels?

Own a George Foreman Grill?

Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
